data.description: ***BACK ON THE MARKET DUE TO THE BUYER'S CHANGE OF CIRCUMSTANCE. ***  NO FLOOD ZONE! STUNNING HOME IN THE HIGHLY DESIRABLE ST. PETERSBURG AREA!  Looking for nature close to the city?   Less than 5 minutes to the Pinellas Trail, only 10 minutes to beautiful Gulf beaches, a close ride to Downtown St. Petersburg, easy drive to I-275 and 2 international airports.   This move-in ready house in a quiet neighborhood represents a great opportunity to own a piece of real estate in a prime location.   Newly renovated and updated to reflect modern vibe, this home boasts a practical layout, featuring a specious living/family room combo with crown moldings, large kitchen with all solid wood cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, dining room, and a half bathroom, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quality time with family. 2022 refinished terrazzo floors provide easy-to -maintain surface throughout all ground floor. The second floor Owners’ suite has a walk-in closet and attached 2023 totally renovated en-suite bathroom. Three additional bedrooms and another 2023 updated bathroom are also upstairs. Many ceiling fans enhance airflow while the central air conditioning and heating system ensure year-round comfort. The house is fortified with R38 energy rated attic insulation. The upgrades in this home speak volume and also include 2020 Roof, 2020 4-ton Heat Pump Condenser, 2021 vinyl soffits, 2021 exterior paint, 2022 change to circular and paved driveway, 2023 white vinyl fence, 2023 2nd floor interior paint.  The property is fully fenced and the oversized double side gate allows for RV, Boat or any other toy’s parking and storage. The private rear yard can nicely accommodate a generous pool. The assigned school zone consists of A+ schools.  Do not miss this rare chance to reside in charming and elegant Bear Creek Estates. This is truly one of the kind property that delivers value and style.                 Your St. Petersburg gem awaits, call today for your private showing!
